texts.text: Patch 36 was a version of Wii U Edition released on July 31, 2018.[1] [edit]

Added the Super Cute Texture Pack.[1]
Added Skin Pack 2.[1]

Xbox 360 Edition TU67

"An update for Minecraft Console Edition on Sony consoles is rolling out now in Europe and Japan, and later today in North America. The update is also out now for Wii U, and later for Xbox 360. This update enables the Super Cute Texture Pack, and also Skin Pack 2 for Wii U." – @4JStudios on Twitter, July 31, 2018
